Flickr::Upload
==============

Uploader for flickr.com

INSTALLATION
============

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
============

- LWP
- XML::Parser::Lite::Tree

Completely unrelated to Flickr::API.

EXAMPLES
========

flickr_upload is a completely functional batch uploading tool. There's also
a good amount of examples included as tests in t/ of the source
distribution. And you can always ask me how to do something if it's not
obvious. I might even know.

A perl Tk-based GUI uploader, thickr_upload, is included. To run it,
you may need to install the following additional packages:

	Tk
	Tk::JPEG
	Tk::PNG

